<plot>A fascinating insight into the similarities of beaches all over the world. The four Host will take us on their own journey from sun up to sunset. Presented in the form of a video postcard, 24 hours on the beach will be reflected on in one hour, revealing the video-diarists raw responses to the location. Each diarist is a complete stranger to the beach they have been sent to and throughout the program parallels and differences between the beaches will be the basis of the Beach Diary journey.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?061881</url></doc>
